2. **AI Efficiency** – Use AI tools (ChatGPT, Gemini, Jasper) to analyze & rewrite resumes for ATS (Applicant Tracking System) compatibility and keyword optimization.  
3. **Low Startup Cost** – Only need a website (Wix/Squarespace), AI subscriptions (~$50/month), and basic marketing.  
4. **Scalable** – Can expand to cover other industries (finance, healthcare, etc.).  

